t%20sufficient.%20We%20needed%20market%20linkage%20and%20support%20to%20solve%20livelihood%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Suhas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20has%20prevented%208%2C000%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste%20from%20entering%20the%20landfills%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Frag-dolls-2-1719483072-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20has%20prevented%208%2C000%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste%20from%20entering%20the%20landfills%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20need%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegooddoll.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Good%20Gift%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20early%202023.%20Serving%20as%20the%20marketing%20arm%20of%20the%20Indian%20Yards%20Foundation%2C%20the%20startup%20fosters%20economic%20empowerment%20of%20tribal%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20created%20a%20website%20to%20take%20the%20product%20to%20the%20market.%20Everything%20was%20flowing%20smoothly%20but%20we%20still%20had%20not%20reached%20our%20hero%20product.%20So%2C%20we%20experimented%20with%20multiple%20products%20and%20finally%20zeroed%20in%20on%20fabric%20dolls%20and%20toys%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sunita.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20growing%20segment%20which%20is%20moving%20away%20from%20plastic%2C%20and%20parents%20do%20not%20want%20their%20children%20playing%20with%20plastic%20toys%20anymore%20as%20they%20are%20not%20only%20hazardous%20to%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20to%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20sustainability%20intrinsic%20to%20the%20brand%2C%20the%20couple%20strived%20to%20hand%20craft%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F240181%2Fsmriti-lamech-prowess-kodaikanal-dolls-kalpana-chawla-savitribai-phule-frida-kahlo-india-vid01%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efabric%20dolls%20%3C%2Fa%3Eusing%20upcycled%20textile%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20buying%20new%20raw%20material%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20as%20sustainable%20as%20possible.%20In%20garment%20factories%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20waste%20post%20production%20and%20not%20all%20of%20the%20material%20is%20utilised.%20So%2C%20we%20retrieve%20off-cuts%20from%20the%20bedsheets%20and%20cushions%2C%20excess%20material%2C%20fabric%20with%20wrong%20prints%20from%20factories%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Sunita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20focussed%20on%20keeping%20their%20fabric%20dolls%20body%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC41-o7gy7ec%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC41-o7gy7ec%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C