chemicals%2C%20mattresses%2C%20leather%20upholstery%3B%20even%20the%20automobile%20industry!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20her%20company%2C%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%2C%20has%20created%2040%20products%20using%20their%20active%20copper%20technology.%20They%20also%20closed%20their%20maiden%20funding%20round%20of%20Rs%203.13%20crore%20with%20the%20Indian%20angel%20network%20and%20IIM%20Lucknow.%20This%20will%20give%20a%20fillip%20to%20their%20mission%20of%20preventing%20imports%20in%20niche%20material%20science%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20India%20Aatmanirbhar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnasuya%20pursued%20an%20MTech%20in%20Fibre%20Science%20and%20Technology%20from%20IIT-Delhi%2C%20post%20which%20she%20enrolled%20for%20a%20PhD%20program%20in%20the%20same%20institution%20from%202014%20to%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20her%20PhD%20course%20that%20she%20had%20a%20significant%20realisation%20%E2%80%94%20she%20wanted%20to%20make%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20beyond%20academia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20researching%20antimicrobial%20materials%2C%20focusing%20especially%20on%20polymers.%20The%20focus%20of%20my%20doctoral%20research%20was%20developing%20such%20materials.%20While%20we%20worked%20with%20different%20inorganic%20materials%20like%20silver%2C%20copper%2C%20our%20major%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20antimicrobial%20properties%20of%20copper%20nanoparticles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20research%20focused%20on%20developing%20antimicrobial%20materials%20that%20could%20inhibit%20the%20growth%20of%20microorganisms.%20In%20her%20final%20year%20of%20doctoral%20research%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20develop%20indigenous%20antimicrobial%20technologies%20that%20would%20provide%20solutions%20across%20different%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anasuya%20developed%20the%20patented%20innovation%20with%20Professor%20Mangala%20Joshi%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-26-at-16.41.42-1719410219-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnasuya%20developed%20the%20patented%20innovation%20with%20Professor%20Mangala%20Joshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20received%20a%20Biotechnology%20Ignition%20Grant%20(BIG)%20from%20the%20Biotechnology%20Industry%20Research%20Assistance%20Council%20(BIRAC)%20in%202019%2C%20which%20helped%20kick%20off%20her%20venture.%20Besides%20spending%20time%20at%20the%20lab%2C%20she%20also%20spent%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20time%20in%20the%20industrial%20area%20of%20Bawana%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20machinery%20helped%20me%20formulate%20the%20venture%20in%20an%20industrially-compatible%20manner.%20Beyond%20my%20work%20at%20the%20lab%2C%20it%20took%20me%20almost%20a%20year%20to%20understand%20the%20process%20on%20ground.%20In%20this%20one%20year%20of%20incubation%2C%20I%20understood%20how%20I%20wanted%20to%20produce%20the%20anti-microbial%20technology%20for%20different%20industries%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20engineer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20worked%20on%20her%20startup%20baby%2C%20she%20also%20became%20a%20mother.%20By%20March%202020%2C%20she%20had%20all%20the%20processes%20figured%20out%20and%20was%20near-ready%20to%20start%20production.%20And%20what%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20were%20the%20antimicrobial%20masks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20technology%3F%20Why%20copper%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%E2%80%99s%20patented%20technology%20is%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352011%2Fnikhil-kumar-chintan-prajapati-greenevo-bio-bottles-plastic-free-sugarcane-biodegradable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactive%20copper%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20protects%20against%20the%20different%20microbes%20like%20bacteria%2C%20virus%2C%20fungi%20and%20algae%20in%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-36-1719410198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20micronutrient%20and%20has%20antimicrobial%20properties.%20This%20makes%20our%20technology%20safe%20and%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECopper%20in%20India%20is%20generally%20used%20for%20disinfection%20because%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98purifying%E2%80%99%20properties%20as%20per%20traditional%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20technology%20which%20stems%20from%20the%20traditional%20science%20that%20advocates%20the%20use%20of%20copper%20for%20the%20purification%20of%20water.%20We%20have%20synthesised%20it%20to%20act%20against%20four%20different%20microbes%20%E2%80%94%20bacteria%2C%20virus%2C%20fungi%20and%20algae.%20While%20most%20companies%20act%20only%20against%20one%20of%20the%20four%2C%20we%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20working%20against%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Anasuya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20four%20patents%20for%20the%20usage%20of%20active%20copper%20in%20different%20ways.%20The%20founder%20also%20shares%20that%20what%20makes%20the%20technology%20unique%20is%20copper%2C%20the%20core%20ingredient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20technologies%20based%20on%20silver.%20While%20nano%20silver%20is%20toxic%20for%20human%20consumption%2C%20copper%20is%20safe%20on%20all%20these%20parameters%3B%20is%20sustainable%20and%20is%20also%20an%20essential%20micronutrient%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20technology%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20active%20copper%20to%20disinfect%20the%20product%20from%20microbes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%E2%80%99s%20patented%20process%20synthesises%20source%20copper%20into%20active%20micro-size%20particles%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20create%20formulations%20in%20powder%2C%20liquid%20and%20other%20forms%2C%20which%20then%20kill%20the%20microbes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20particles%20are%20then%20combined%20with%20other%20materials%20to%20produce%20commercially-viable%20products.%20These%20products%20are%20used%20across%20different%20materials%20like%20plastic%2C%20foam%2C%20textiles%2C%20polymers%2C%20paints%2C%20coatings%20and%20cosmetics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20our%20formulations%20are%20substantiated%20across%20different%20ISO%20(International%20Organisation%20for%20Standardisation)%20and%20ASTM%20(American%20Society%20for%20Testing%20and%20Materials)%20testing%20standards%20with%20consistent%2099.99%25%20antimicrobial%20activity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOff%20the%20beaten%20track%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20selling%20masks%2C%20she%20was%20introduced%20to%20her%20co-founder%20Nirav%20Mehta%2C%20who%20suggested%C2%A0%20pivoting%20to%20other%20industries.%20They%20diversified%20to%20plastic%2C%20polymer%20materials%2C%20starting%20with%20water%20tanks%20and%20pipes%2C%20which%20are%20prone%20to%20microbial%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20water%20segment%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20foam%20used%20in%20mattresses%2C%20where%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20need%20for%20disinfection.%20They%20are%20now%20also%20working%20with%20automobile%20companies%20to%20make%20the%20frequent%20touch%20points%20inside%20antimicrobial.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20customers%20include%20Astral%20Pipes%2C%20Supreme%2C%20LG%20and%20more.%20The%20scientist%20adds%20that%20they%20customise%20the%20technology%20based%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20customer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanosafe%20has%20won%20several%20awards%20for%20its%20pioneering%20technology%20including%20the%20National%20Start%20Up%20Award%202023%20and%20the%20National%20Technology%20Excellence%20Award%202022%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Anasuya%20wants%20Nanosafe%20to%20become%20a%20powerhouse%20in%20the%20material%20science%E2%80%99s%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20on%20building%20other%20niche%20technologies%20to%20champion%20the%20cause%20of%20import%20substitution%20and%20export%20promotion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719411948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Putting%20her%20PhD%20thesis%20to%20practical%20use%2C%20Dr%20Anasuya%20Roy%20launched%20Nanosafe%20Solutions.%20Her%20company%20uses%20a%20patented%20antimicrobial%20active%20copper%20technology%20to%20disinfect%20everything%20from%20water%20bottles%20and%20cosmetics%20to%20textiles%20and%20polymers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Monsoon%2C%20%23DonateARoof%20To%20Help%20200%20Underprivileged%20Kids%20Study%20in%20Safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20years%20from%20now%2C%20you%20will%20spot%20a%20young%20journalist%20on%20television.%20Watch%20out%20for%20%E2%80%98Sakshi%20Patel%E2%80%99%2C%20whose%20factual%20reporting%20style%20on%20the%20issues%20encountered%20by%20remote%20Indian%20villages%20will%20take%20you%20by%20surprise.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20mincing%20of%20words%20as%20she%20digs%20out%20solutions%20to%20the%20daily%20battles%20fought%20by%20children%20in%20these%20rural%20hinterlands%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20education.%20Sakshi%20will%20demand%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20stories%20will%20be%20tinged%20with%20personal%20experience.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20is%20speaking%20about%20a%20subject%20close%20to%20her%20heart.%20Sakshi%20Patel%20will%20be%20a%20name%20to%20reckon%20with%20%E2%80%94%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FDonate-To-Build-Roof%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FDonate-To-Build-Roof%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20right%20now%20she%20is%20just%20a%20little%20girl%20with%20big%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296487%2Fvideo-volunteers-helps-rescue-bonded-labourers-ngo-journalists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edreams%20of%20becoming%20a%20journalist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20she%20tells%20me.%20The%20Jansa%20village%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20she%20lives%2C%20is%20home%20to%20a%20number%20of%20children%20like%20her%3B%20children%20whose%20parents%20are%20engaged%20in%20odd%20jobs%20such%20as%20boring%20wells%2C%20building%20homes%20and%20stone%20cutting%2C%20cleaning%20lakes%20and%20flower%20selling%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghats%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20area%20leading%20to%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20holy%20Ganges%20river).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20is%20a%20firm%20believer%20that%20simply%20dreaming%20is%20not%20enough%3B%20one%20has%20to%20act%20on%20these%20dreams%20for%20them%20to%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-year-old%20girl%20is%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Jansa%