20solutions%20to%20rural%20and%20urban%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20large%20boats%20were%20equipped%20with%20solar%20panels%20of%203%20KV%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20solar%20power%20can%E2%80%99t%20drive%20vessels%20on%20a%20river%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20So%2C%20we%20use%20it%20to%20run%20lighting%20and%20basic%20services%20like%20fans.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20cold%20chains%20for%20chilling%20units%20which%20store%20and%20carry%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-saving%20equipment%20are%20also%20solar-powered%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-5-1719399732-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20rows%20from%20village%20to%20village%20across%20the%20district%20organising%20health%20camps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiturekha%20says%20that%20with%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20crew%20has%20an%20uninter