20a%20cardboard%20sheet%20with%20her%20plan%2C%20listing%20the%20subjects%20and%20organising%20them%20into%20six%20columns.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20column%20was%20study%2C%20second%20notes%2C%20third%20was%20revision%20one%2C%20fourth%20was%20revision%20two%2C%20fifth%20was%20crisp%20notes%2C%20and%20sixth%20was%20final%20revision.%20For%20each%20subject%2C%20I%20would%20place%20a%20tick%20once%20I%20completed%20each%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taruni's%20time%20table%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-10-1719322769-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354316%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20time%20table.%20List%20down%20the%20subjects%20and%20tick%20the%20items%20after%20completion.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paucity%20of%20time%20meant%20that%20the%20aspirant%20had%20to%20make%20detailed%20notes%20to%20aid%20in%20quick%20revisions.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20made%20schematic%20or%20diagrammatic%20notes%20and%20acronyms%20for%20each%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20notes%20were%20very%20concise.%20My%20public%20administration%20notes%20only%20had%20four%20pages!%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20chuckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20every%20week%2C%20Taruni%20evaluated%20her%20progress%20using%20a%20carrot-and-stick%20approach.%20She%20would%20sit%20with%20a%20pen%20and%20tick%20off%20completed%20tasks%20from%20her%20plan.%20For%20sticking%20to%20the%20plan%2C%20she%20rewarded%20herself%20with%20treats%20like%20a%20movie%20on%20Netflix%20or%20an%20ice%20cream.%20As%20a%20punishment%20for%20not%20meeting%20her%20goals%2C%20she%20would%20forgo%20her%20beloved%20tea%20or%20coffee%20for%20the%20entire%20weekend%20or%20sometimes%20stay%20off%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sounds%20a%20word%20of%20warning%20though%3A%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20are%20watching%20something%20online%2C%20stick%20to%20light-hearted%20comedies.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20go%20for%20a%20series%20or%20anything%20that%20is%20addictive%20or%20will%20distract%20you.%20No%20binge-watching.%20If%20I%20were%20an%20aspirant%20today%2C%20I%20would%20have%20probably%20chosen%20something%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ELaapata%20Ladies%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20This%20motivational%20approach%2C%20she%20explains%2C%20rewires%20your%20brain%20and%20forces%20you%20to%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwDQY1VIO1P%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwDQY1VIO1P%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%